## 📋 Quick Reference Checklist

Before implementing any feature or fix:

- [ ] Does this follow existing codebase patterns?
- [ ] Is this the simplest solution that works?
- [ ] Have I tested this to ensure no regressions?
- [ ] Is this accessible (WCAG 2.1 AA)?
- [ ] Is this responsive (mobile-first)?
- [ ] Is this performant (meets Core Web Vitals)?
- [ ] Is this secure (no XSS, CSRF, injection risks)?
- [ ] Is this documented (code comments, README updates)?
- [ ] Have I considered edge cases and error states?
- [ ] Does this follow SOLID principles?
- [ ] Is there any code duplication that should be extracted?
- [ ] Are there any magic numbers/strings that should be constants?
- [ ] Is the code self-documenting with meaningful names?
- [ ] Have I checked for similar patterns elsewhere in the codebase?
- [ ] Is this a workaround? If so, is it documented with proper solution plan?
